casebody.data:
Thursday, November 19, 1992

MOTION DOCKET

92-2252. Consumers’ Counsel v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 91-1648-TP-ATA. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for stay,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said motion for stay be, and the same is hereby, denied.

Moyer, C.J., and Resnick, J., not participating.
